  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Babushka</strong> is a first-person horror game about an old grandmother whom her grandson—the player—must rescue. The player needs to find her stolen and lost belongings and rebuild her old house in an ancient town, all while avoiding strange townsfolk and monsters from the underworld.</p>",
